data.title: Rahul Mahajan Ties The Knot For The 3rd Time With His 25-Year-Old Girlfriend Natalya Ilina
data.meta_description: this article talks about ex bigg boss contestant rahul mahajn tying the knot for the 3rd time with his girl friend from Kazakhstan named natalya ilina. He was previously married to dimpy ganguly
data.text:
Seems like 'once bitten, twice shy' is not something Rahul Mahajn believes in. The ex-Bigg Boss contestant has been making it to the news in the past several years for just one reason- his relationships! The man was married twice in the past and as per reports, both his ex-wives accused him of domestic violence.

He was married to Shweta Singh and then reportedly had a brief attachment to fellow contestant Monica Bedi when they both appeared on the reality show together.

Later, Rahul participated in another reality show which was a 'Swayamvar' and there he fell for the pretty Dimpy Ganguly. They were married for over 5 years but their marriage was pretty turbulent, something which Dimpy spoke about often after they separated.
